track_notes: Nice panorama on summit, the sight is from sea to hight summits of the Alpes.
track_title: easiest and shortest path to the summit

track_notes:
You can start the walk from a lot of place nearby the village; there is no problem to park the car.
The panorama from the summit is very fine, as you can see the beach on one side and the ski resort on the other one.
Funny circuit witch looks as an eight.. I started there because i was short of time; But in fact i spent more time driving on the forest road than walking from the parking. Nice place to be

You can start the walk from the village, if you come by bus from Nice, or you can park at the car-park. just follow the red+white paint. If you are curious you can visit a large cave on your way to the summit.
Easy walk from another starting point
Not so easy, because of the way down can be difficult if the ground is wet.
